'''宇宙紅移7號星系'''（{{lang-en|Cosmos Redshift 7}}），是一個位於[[六分儀座|六分儀座]]的[[紅移#外星系的觀察|高紅移]]（[[紅移#測量、特性和解釋|z]] ∼ 6−7）{{註|越高紅移就代表該天體距離地球越遠，即意味著宇宙紅移7號星系是宇宙上最古老與遙遠的星系之一。}}[[萊曼α發射體|萊曼α發射體]][[星系|星系]]，距離地球至少129億[[光年|光年]]。該星系包含在[[大爆炸|大爆炸]]之後不久的[[再電離|再電離]]時期所形成的第一批恆星（第一代的[[第三星族星|第三星族星]]）與它們於大約8億年前所產生出的[[化學元素|化學元素]]（[[氧|氧]]，[[氮|氮]]，[[碳|碳]]，[[鈣|鈣]]和[[鐵|鐵]]等），而這些元素是後來形成星球與生命的關鍵<ref name="AJ-20150604">{{cite journal |last1=Sobral |first1=David |last2=Matthee |first2=Jorryt |last3=Darvish |first3=Behnam |last4=Schaerer |first4=Daniel |last5=Mobasher |first5=Bahram |last6=Röttgering |first6=Huub J. A. |last7=Santos |first7=Sérgio |last8=Hemmati |first8=Shoubaneh |title=Evidence For POPIII-Like Stellar Populations In The Most Luminous LYMAN-α Emitters At The Epoch Of Re-Ionisation: Spectroscopic Confirmation |url=http://arxiv.org/pdf/1504.01734.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |date=4 June 2015 |journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]] |accessdate=17 June 2015 |archive-date=2015-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904042713/http://arxiv.org/pdf/1504.01734.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT-20150617">{{cite news |last=Overbye |first=Dennis |authorlink= |title=Astronomers Report Finding Earliest Stars That Enriched Cosmos |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/18/science/space/astronomers-report-finding-earliest-stars-that-enriched-cosmos.html |date=17 June 2015 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=17 June 2015 |archive-date=2019-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203002025/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/18/science/space/astronomers-report-finding-earliest-stars-that-enriched-cosmos.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ESO-20160617">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=ESO1524 — Science Release - Best Observational Evidence of First Generation Stars in the Universe |url=http://www.eso.org/public/news/eso1524/ |date=17 June 2015 |work=European Southern Observatory |accessdate=17 June 2015 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330044747/https://www.eso.org/public/news/eso1524/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ES-20150617">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=Brightest galaxy and first-generation stars |url=https://earthsky.org/space/brightest-galaxy-and-first-generation-stars |date=17 June 2015 |work=[[Earth_&_Sky|Earth & Sky]] |accessdate=17 June 2015 |archive-date=2018-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805001714/http://earthsky.org/space/brightest-galaxy-and-first-generation-stars |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="UCR-20150617">{{cite web |last=Pittalwala |first=Iqbal |title=Astronomers Find Best Observational Evidence of First Generation Stars in the Universe |url=http://ucrtoday.ucr.edu/29947 |date=17 June 2015 |work=University of California, Riverside |accessdate=17 June 2015 |archive-date=2018-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180518231446/https://ucrtoday.ucr.edu/29947 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

== 概述 ==
宇宙紅移7號星系有著[[金屬量|第二星族]]（貧金屬星）與[[第三星族星|第三星族]]（無金屬星）的星，天文學家們發現它時檢測出它的光度比當時最亮的遙遠星系還高出三倍<ref name="AJ-20150604" /><ref name="NYT-20150617" /><ref name="ESO-20160617" /><ref name="UCR-20150617" /><ref name="MNRAS-20150721">{{cite journal |last1=Matthee |first1=Jorryt |last2=Sobral |first2=David |last3=et al. |journal=[[MNRAS|MNRAS]] |date=21 July 2015 |volume=451 |page=4919-4936 |doi=10.1093/mnras/stv947 |title=Identification of the brightest Lyalpha emitters at z=6.6: implications for the evolution of the luminosity function in the re-ionisation era |12= |url=http://arxiv.org/abs/1502.07355 |bibcode=2015MNRAS.451.4919M |access-date=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2022-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220510022535/https://arxiv.org/abs/1502.07355 }}</ref>。

== 發現與命名 ==
宇宙紅移7號星系是由以大衛·索布拉爾（David Sobral）為首的一班來自[[里斯本|里斯本]]或[[萊頓|萊頓]]的天文學家使用[[歐洲南方天文台|歐洲南方天文台]]的[[甚大望遠鏡|甚大望遠鏡]]（VLT），並經由[[凱克天文台|凱克天文台]]、[[毛納基山天文台|毛納基山天文台]][[昴星團望遠鏡|昴星團望遠鏡]]與[[NASA|NASA]]/[[ESA|ESA]][[哈勃太空望遠鏡|哈勃太空望遠鏡]]的幫助下發現的。該天文學家團隊的成員來自於[[加州大學河濱分校|加州大學河濱分校]]<ref name="UCR-20150617" />、[[日內瓦大學|日內瓦大學]]、[[萊頓大學|萊頓大學]]與[[里斯本大學|里斯本大學]]四間大學<ref name="AJ-20150604" />。

該星系名字的靈感來自於[[葡萄牙國家足球隊|葡萄牙國家足球隊]]與[[皇家馬德里足球俱樂部|皇家馬德里足球俱樂部]]的成員之一，葡萄牙的足球運動員[[克里斯蒂亞諾·羅納度|克里斯蒂亞諾·羅納度]]。他也俗稱「CR7」，而組成宇宙紅移7號星系的英文的各單字字首便為CR7<ref name="ESO-20160617"/><ref>{{cite web |author=Staff |title=Traces of Earliest Stars That Enriched Cosmos Are Spied |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/18/science/space/astronomers-report-finding-earliest-stars-that-enriched-cosmos.html |date=17 June 2015 |accessdate=17 June 2015 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |archive-date=2019-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203002025/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/18/science/space/astronomers-report-finding-earliest-stars-that-enriched-cosmos.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Staff |title=Cristiano Ronaldo: CR7 name given to discovered galaxy |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33185760 |date=18 June 2015 |accessdate=18 June 2015 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] |archive-date=2016-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107100925/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33185760 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Staff |title=Cristiano Ronaldo: CR7 gets his own galaxy |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/18/football/cristiano-ronaldo-galaxy-football/ |date=18 June 2015 |accessdate=18 June 2015 |work=[[CNN|CNN]] |archive-date=2018-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718175916/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/18/football/cristiano-ronaldo-galaxy-football/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

